    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/62cc9385623fd4c07f5e4133774e2684.avif?t=1729731143\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras_big/62cc9385623fd4c07f5e4133774e2684.avif?t=1729731143 width=800 height=375 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Topple Tactics is a physics-based multiplayer tower defense game where one huge player places towers whilst the little players must get to the end of the map in order to defeat the huge player!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/a138ec18cdf4365453ef18bda6313015.avif?t=1729731143\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/fd4e9f47d51de9a82290f1549e805ae0.poster.avif?t=1729731143\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/fd4e9f47d51de9a82290f1549e805ae0.webm?t=1729731143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/fd4e9f47d51de9a82290f1549e805ae0.mp4?t=1729731143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Place and upgrade towers and use your abilities in order to make crossing the map as difficult as possible for the little players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/83a74ca36960d609a531e5d06252e010.avif?t=1729731143\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/bd0f0e932cf67db8e3505e685136be99.poster.avif?t=1729731143\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/bd0f0e932cf67db8e3505e685136be99.webm?t=1729731143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/bd0f0e932cf67db8e3505e685136be99.mp4?t=1729731143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>As a minion in a tower defense track, you must upgrade your player in order to face the increasingly difficult onslaught built by the big player!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/faa0b451783d79a98c5d6189590842bc.avif?t=1729731143\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/423a0c7dbb5ec18a6221f18cffe574a4.poster.avif?t=1729731143\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/423a0c7dbb5ec18a6221f18cffe574a4.webm?t=1729731143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/423a0c7dbb5ec18a6221f18cffe574a4.mp4?t=1729731143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Play on 7 different maps all which require different strategies from both types of players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/89842763826731957e12540df4453175.avif?t=1729731143\" width=800 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/79fb59dcee9867a2a0ab447f2f90d843.poster.avif?t=1729731143\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/79fb59dcee9867a2a0ab447f2f90d843.webm?t=1729731143\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390260/extras/79fb59dcee9867a2a0ab447f2f90d843.mp4?t=1729731143\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>- </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics-based characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvP</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A large tower and ability arsenal for the huge player</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A large upgrade tree for the little player</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character customization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&amp; much more!</p></li></ul>",
